sources.sass\\base\\_typography.sass:
body
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace
    color: var(--primary)
    background: var(--background)
sources.sass\\layout\\_grid.sass:
$grid: map-get($config, grid)
$column: map-get($grid, column)

.row
    display: flex
    flex-wrap: wrap

[class^=col-]
    flex-basis: 100%

@for $i from 1 through $column
    .col-#{$i}
        padding: var(--gap)
        flex: 0 0 100%
        +mq(lg)
            flex: 0 0 (100% / ($column / $i))
    .col-offset-#{$i}
        margin-left: 0
        +mq(lg)
            margin-left: 100% / ($column / $i)
sources.sass\\pages\\demo.sass:
.col
    height: 4rem

    &-content
        display: flex
        align-items: center
        justify-content: center
        color: rgba(white, .6)
        height: 100%

.container
    width: calc(100% - var(--margin)*2)
    max-width: var(--xl)
    margin: 0 auto
